sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant GW as API Gateway / Trigger
    participant FP as FaaS Platform
    participant FN as Function Code

    C->>GW: HTTP request
    GW->>FP: Invoke function with event payload

    alt Cold start - no warm instance
        FP->>FP: Provision execution environment
        FP->>FP: Pull runtime container image
        FP->>FP: Start runtime process
        FP->>FN: Run initialization code
        FN-->>FP: Init complete
        FP->>FN: Invoke handler with event
        FN->>FN: Execute business logic
        FN->>FN: Call downstream services or DB
        FN-->>FP: Return response payload
        FP-->>GW: Function response
        GW-->>C: HTTP response
        FP->>FP: Keep environment warm for reuse
    else Warm start - instance available
        FP->>FN: Invoke handler with event
        FN->>FN: Execute business logic
        FN-->>FP: Return response payload
        FP-->>GW: Function response
        GW-->>C: HTTP response
    end
